title: S&P 500 Movers: TSN, WDC - Nasdaq.com
text: In early trading on Wednesday, shares of Western Digital Corp ( WDC  ) topped the list of the day's best performing components of the S&P 500 index, trading up 6.5%. Year to date, Western Digital Corp registers a 65.5% gain.      And the worst performing S&P 500 component thus far on the day is Tyson Foods ( TSN  ), trading down 4.0%. Tyson Foods is showing a gain of 67.8% looking at the year to date performance.  makeArticleAd();    Two other components making moves today are Starbucks Corp. ( SBUX  ), trading down 3.1%, and PVH Corp ( PVH  ), trading up 6.4% on the day.        VIDEO: S&P 500 Movers: TSN, WDC
